data.description: This newer home, built in 2021 is ready for you!  With over 1.5 acres to enjoy the privacy that Golden Gate Estates offers, this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has a split floor plan, and open kitchen with stainless appliances.  Tray ceilings, granite countertops, and custom tile baths add to the character of this unique property.  Schedule a showing to come and see how you can make this place your home!
